network.postprocessing

Class RerankingResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.postprocessing.RerankingResult

  • public class RerankingResult
extends java.lang.Object
    RerankingResult is a class storing the results of individual re-rankings. It merges new results with previous reranking and can output the final result to the standard TSV format. It was created to avoid storing all NetworkFileBackedWrapper results until they could be merged at the end, which resulted in memory issues.
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Joeri Ruyssinck (joeri.ruysssinck@intec.ugent.be)
